		<updated>2016-03-07T03:16:58+11:00</updated>
		<id>https://sphinx.org.au/the-ark/for-programmers/19-get-the-source-code</id>
		<author>
			<name>Adrian Bickerstaffe</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;The Ark's source code and documentation is hosted by GitHub at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/The-Ark-Informatics/ark&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;this location&lt;/a&gt;. To check out the repository using &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-scm.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Git&lt;/a&gt;, issue the following command:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table style=&quot;background-color: #ededed;&quot; cellpadding=&quot;5&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;git clone &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/The-Ark-Informatics/ark.git&quot;&gt;https://github.com/The-Ark-Informatics/ark.git&lt;/a&gt; TheArk&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The source code can be modified and redistributed under the terms of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.en.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;GNU GPL v3 license&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Ark is built upon open source libraries and frameworks including Apache &lt;a href=&quot;http://wicket.apache.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Wicket&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://shiro.apache.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Shiro&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://spring.io/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Spring&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://hibernate.org/&quot;&gt;Hibernate&lt;/a&gt;. Pedigree visualisation is provided by integration with &lt;a href=&quot;http://madeline.med.umich.edu/madeline/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Madeline&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To become a member of the developer team and contribute to the project, please email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:travis.endersby@uwa.edu.au&quot;&gt;Travis Endersby&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:adrianb@unimelb.edu.au&quot;&gt;Adrian Bickerstaffe&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;The Ark's source code and documentation is hosted by GitHub at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/The-Ark-Informatics/ark&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;this location&lt;/a&gt;. To check out the repository using &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-scm.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Git&lt;/a&gt;, issue the following command:&lt;/p&gt;
